                        <interp inst="t18560514-495-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.† Aged 36.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">MARSHALL</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18560514-495-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
